WEBVTT

00:03:58.130 --> 00:04:01.263
Skupaj sem pripeljala
antropologe, epidemiologe,

00:04:01.297 --> 00:04:02.930
psihologe,

00:04:02.963 --> 00:04:05.963
poznavalce digitalnih medijev

00:04:05.997 --> 00:04:08.363
in strokovnjake za matematične modele.

00:04:08.363 --> 00:04:10.730
Zadali smo si nalogo,

00:04:10.763 --> 00:04:15.197
da raziščemo epizode
govoric skozi zgodovino

00:04:15.197 --> 00:04:17.030
ter njihov vpliv.

00:04:17.030 --> 00:04:20.963
Iskali smo zgodnje znake,

00:04:20.997 --> 00:04:22.963
dejavnike, ki so govorice okrepili,

00:04:22.997 --> 00:04:24.597
njihov vpliv,

00:04:24.630 --> 00:04:26.430
kako so se oprijele,

00:04:26.463 --> 00:04:30.363
da bi razumeli, kaj moramo iskati,